{"id": "art-5341", "label": "Art. 5341", "title": "Art. 5341: Informaţii referitoare la raportul de serviciu al funcţionarului public", "slug": "art-5341", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_798680400\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1126\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_798680400\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 534<sup>1</sup>:\nInforma&#355;ii referitoare la raportul de serviciu al func&#355;ionarului\npublic </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_707226230\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1125\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_707226230\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Persoana care are\ncompeten&#355;a legal&#259; de numire sau, dup&#259; caz, conduc&#259;torul\nautorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice trebuie s&#259; informeze\nfunc&#355;ionarul public cu privire la urm&#259;toarele elemente:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_592880204\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1124\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_592880204\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)dreptul la formare &#351;i perfec&#355;ionare\nprofesional&#259;, asigurat de autoritatea sau institu&#355;ia public&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1802132263\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1123\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1802132263\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)durata concediului de odihn&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1315281852\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1122\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1315281852\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)condi&#355;iile de acordare a preavizului &#351;i durata\nperioadei de preaviz;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2102809478\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1121\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2102809478\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)data pl&#259;&#355;ii salariului &#351;i metoda de\nplat&#259; a salariului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_525797012\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1120\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_525797012\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)modalitatea de efectuare a orelor suplimentare,\nremunera&#355;ia acestora sau, dup&#259; caz, compensarea prin ore libere\npl&#259;tite;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_517111855\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1119\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_517111855\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)acordurile colective încheiate de autoritatea sau\ninstitu&#355;ia public&#259;, în condi&#355;iile art. 487, cu sindicatul\nreprezentativ al func&#355;ionarilor publici la nivel de autoritate sau\ninstitu&#355;ie public&#259;, sindicatul afiliat la o federa&#355;ie\nreprezentativ&#259; la nivelul sectorului de activitate din care face parte\nautoritatea sau institu&#355;ia public&#259; sau sindicatul afiliat la o\nfedera&#355;ie reprezentativ&#259; la nivelul grupului de unit&#259;&#355;i din\ncare face parte autoritatea sau institu&#355;ia public&#259;, dup&#259; caz,\nori cu reprezentan&#355;ii func&#355;ionarilor publici;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_672925080\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1118\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_672925080\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)contribu&#355;ii suplimentare la pensia facultativ&#259;\nsau la pensia ocupa&#355;ional&#259; a func&#355;ionarului public suportate de\nautoritatea sau institu&#355;ia public&#259;, în condi&#355;iile legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1780917330\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1117\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1780917330\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)Regulamentul de organizare &#351;i func&#355;ionare al\nautorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice &#351;i regulamentul intern\nal autorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_312932192\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1116\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_312932192\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Formatul standard al informa&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute\nla alin. (1) se stabile&#351;te prin ordin al pre&#351;edintelui Agen&#355;iei\nNa&#355;ionale a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici, care se public&#259; în Monitorul\nOficial al României, Partea I.</span></p>"}